[32m│[0m (SSRF)** vulnerabilities                                                     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **3. Security Implications:**                                                [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - The ability to store arbitrary URLs that the server will process opens     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m potential SSRF attack vectors                                                [32m│[0m
