[32m│[0m http://flask_app:8080)                                                       [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 3. Changes persist and can be retrieved via /api/get                         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 4. No authentication required                                                [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m This is an **SSRF (Server-Side Request Forgery)** vulnerability created by   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m "over-securing" - the developer tried to make a generic, flexible URL system [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m but created a way to access internal services.                               [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
