[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ## SSRF Testing Results                                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Status Code**: 404 Not Found (all attempts)                                [32m│[0m
