[32m│[0m ## SSRF Test Results                                                         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m I tested the flask_app:8080/health endpoint through SSRF by:                 [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 1. Setting the URL via `/api/set?url=http://flask_app:8080/health`           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 2. Triggering the SSRF via GET `/app`                                        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### Detailed Summary                                                         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **SSRF Configuration Phase:**                                                [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Successfully set API URL to `http://flask_app:8080/health`                 [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Response: `HTTP/1.1 200 OK` with confirmation "API URL set to:             [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m http://flask_app:8080/health"                                                [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **SSRF Trigger Phase:**                                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Triggered SSRF via GET `/app` endpoint                                     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Response: `HTTP/1.1 500 INTERNAL SERVER ERROR` (17,515 bytes)              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - **Root Cause**: The application expects JSON with a "script" field but     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m received non-JSON content                                                    [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Traceback reveals the app flow:                                            [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m   1. Fetches URL from `http://nginx/api/get`                                 [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m   2. Makes request to the configured URL (flask_app:8080/health)             [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m   3. Attempts `eval(json.loads(script)["script"])`                           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m   4. Fails with `JSONDecodeError: Expecting value: line 1 column 1 (char 0)` [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Key Finding**: The `/health` endpoint likely returns plain text (not JSON  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m with "script" field), causing the JSON parsing failure.                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
